---
title: Smart Ground Double Pork Taco-Inspired Salad with Chipotle Sauce and Crispy Shallots
description: In this taco-inspired salad, spiced pork is tossed with dressed spinach but it's the toppings that make this dish a true stand-out: feta, crispy shallots, guacamole and cilantro.
